WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.230 --> 02:49.890
[Episode 2]

02:50.690 --> 02:52.970
Looking at this extravagant style

02:52.990 --> 02:55.100
and untamed demeanor,

02:55.300 --> 02:56.810
is this really belonging to an immortal?

02:57.120 --> 02:58.840
I'll have to find out.

03:07.310 --> 03:08.900
Ms. Bai, you said you would come another day.

03:08.930 --> 03:10.360
I thought you would come a few days later.

03:10.560 --> 03:11.890
I didn't realize it was so urgent.

03:12.170 --> 03:13.330
I also didn't expect that

03:13.360 --> 03:14.420
you would remember what I said

03:14.440 --> 03:16.920
despite our brief meeting.

03:17.120 --> 03:18.190
Last night, you said

03:18.210 --> 03:20.100
you are devoted to the pursuit of enlightenment and possess remarkable skills.

03:20.280 --> 03:21.990
I am free to test you however I wish.

03:22.470 --> 03:23.120
In that case...

03:23.140 --> 03:23.810
Wait.

03:25.320 --> 03:26.600
That was last night.

03:26.620 --> 03:28.060
Today is today.

03:28.090 --> 03:29.810
Let's not rush into talking about unrelated matters.

03:29.829 --> 03:31.600
Since we are destined to meet,

03:31.630 --> 03:33.750
we should at least get to know each other.

03:33.910 --> 03:34.910
Here in Ning'an City,

03:34.910 --> 03:36.440
there's a drinking tradition to spice things up.

03:36.460 --> 03:37.860
One shot for one question.

03:38.280 --> 03:39.350
If I drink,

03:39.380 --> 03:40.350
you'll have to answer.

03:40.370 --> 03:41.250
Would you take on the challenge?

03:53.720 --> 03:55.160
You were extraordinary at first sight.

03:55.680 --> 03:57.880
May I know your name and which lineage and sect you are from?

03:57.900 --> 03:59.810
What are you doing here in my city?

03:59.840 --> 04:01.010
I am Fan Yue.

04:01.450 --> 04:04.080
I trained under the previous Sect Leader of the Lanling Sect.

04:04.200 --> 04:05.910
I've spent many years in spiritual cultivation, traveled far and wide,

04:06.040 --> 04:07.210
and I am just passing through this place.

04:07.500 --> 04:09.340
How lucky I must be to be able to meet you.

04:09.360 --> 04:10.800
I caught you even when you're traveling.

04:16.870 --> 04:18.070
I've been seeking immortality for years.

04:18.070 --> 04:19.560
Although I haven't mastered the art of immortality,

04:19.829 --> 04:22.070
I have some knowledge in these matters.

04:23.000 --> 04:25.290
There are many swindlers nowadays.

04:25.510 --> 04:27.240
Since you are so famous,

04:27.240 --> 04:29.430
it's not too much to show me your skills, right?

04:29.430 --> 04:30.780
How dare you compare me

04:30.930 --> 04:32.960
to those wandering charlatans?

04:33.050 --> 04:34.240
Of course not.

04:34.850 --> 04:36.860
As an immortal, you are definitely different from them.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.040
The problem is on me.

04:38.070 --> 04:40.240
I’ve learned to be wary after being deceived many times.

04:40.240 --> 04:41.830
I have to learn to be smart.

04:41.880 --> 04:43.159
If I've offended you,

04:43.159 --> 04:45.070
I'll drink this to make amends.

04:45.340 --> 04:46.930
What do you want to see, Ms. Bai?

04:47.870 --> 04:50.510
Summoning the wind and rain, wielding thunder and lightning.

04:51.020 --> 04:52.130
Are these...

04:52.159 --> 04:53.350
too hard for you?

05:00.770 --> 05:02.480
-What's with the rain?
-It's pouring!

05:05.950 --> 05:06.870
Hurry! Hurry!

05:09.350 --> 05:10.580
Rain conjured by demon aura?

05:11.210 --> 05:12.870
There are demons in the city?

05:12.870 --> 05:14.090
Why is it suddenly raining?

05:14.120 --> 05:14.930
This...

05:16.190 --> 05:18.120
Chong Zhao, you just came back. Where are you going?

05:18.120 --> 05:19.560
Take an umbrella with you.

05:26.030 --> 05:27.540
What else do you want to see, Ms. Bai?

05:28.270 --> 05:30.510
Flames sweeping through the city, and pests plaguing the land?

05:30.730 --> 05:31.850
I'll show you everything

05:31.880 --> 05:33.380
you desire.

05:35.150 --> 05:36.270
It's enough.

05:36.290 --> 05:37.409
You immortals are powerful.

05:37.440 --> 05:38.230
I believe you now.

05:41.270 --> 05:42.880
As for this third toast...

05:48.909 --> 05:50.350
You've asked so many questions.

05:50.380 --> 05:51.770
It's my turn now.

05:55.090 --> 05:55.909
What are you doing?

06:00.690 --> 06:02.280
She's indeed capable.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.190
Don't move.

06:06.920 --> 06:08.180
What is he doing?

06:08.490 --> 06:10.330
Is this a test of my competencies?

06:26.900 --> 06:27.650
Strange.

06:28.730 --> 06:31.170
Why can she trigger a reaction from the Desireless Stone,

06:31.200 --> 06:32.960
but not activate it?

06:33.980 --> 06:35.920
Is it because her contemplation power is too weak?

06:39.300 --> 06:41.440
[Unbridled Pavilion]

06:48.190 --> 06:49.420
[Unbridled Pavilion]

07:15.460 --> 07:17.630
So this is a demon's den.

07:18.240 --> 07:19.160
Kill!

07:21.510 --> 07:22.510
Which respectable sect

07:22.510 --> 07:23.920
would act like this?

07:24.770 --> 07:26.120
Don't fret, Ms. Bai.

07:26.620 --> 07:28.260
This part of Lanling Sect's cultivation techniques.

07:28.730 --> 07:30.020
Forget it if you don't want to learn it.

07:30.050 --> 07:31.520
Do you think I'm stupid?

07:31.590 --> 07:33.350
I've never heard of any sect's magic that

07:33.370 --> 07:35.409
requires a stone to be press against a person's head.

07:35.830 --> 07:37.120
What disciple of the immortals?

07:37.120 --> 07:38.760
You seem more like a demon to me.

07:38.790 --> 07:40.670
The world is full of surprises.

07:40.900 --> 07:42.130
If you have never heard,

07:42.159 --> 07:43.640
it just means you're ignorant.

07:44.159 --> 07:45.200
Ms. Bai.

07:45.220 --> 07:47.070
I sympathize with your pursuit of enlightenment,

07:47.100 --> 07:48.690
so I made an exception to meet you.

07:48.710 --> 07:49.760
If you are not willing,

07:50.370 --> 07:51.370
please leave.

08:24.720 --> 08:25.750
Lanling Sword Technique?

08:26.230 --> 08:27.600
He is from Lanling Sect?

08:36.000 --> 08:36.880
Zhao?

08:39.070 --> 08:40.230
What brings you here?

08:45.270 --> 08:46.870
The Lanling Sect...

08:47.720 --> 08:49.520
They've actually tracked us down?

08:49.550 --> 08:51.180
What a strong aura!

08:51.220 --> 08:53.240
This person seems unfathomable.

08:53.510 --> 08:54.780
He must have used his powers,

08:54.960 --> 08:56.680
for there is no trace of demonic aura.

08:59.740 --> 09:00.740
Who is this?

09:00.770 --> 09:02.020
I’m Chong Zhao.

09:02.040 --> 09:04.120
I’m Bai Shuo’s fiancé, betrothed since childhood.

09:07.030 --> 09:08.270
How interesting.

09:08.980 --> 09:11.300
Who would have thought that such different individuals would be engaged?

09:12.120 --> 09:13.240
Could it be that...

09:13.650 --> 09:15.700
Ms. Bai is someone special?

09:16.360 --> 09:18.320
Bai Shuo is just my fiancée.

09:18.340 --> 09:19.640
She has no special identity.

09:20.480 --> 09:22.850
The elders of my family are worried

09:22.870 --> 09:24.020
about us coming here.

09:24.630 --> 09:26.430
No matter what your intention is,

09:26.610 --> 09:28.070
today is not the right time.

09:29.370 --> 09:30.750
You're right.

09:31.120 --> 09:32.460
We are just passing through,

09:32.720 --> 09:34.490
merely doing some honest work.

09:34.830 --> 09:36.710
Mr. Chong Zhao, if you come again,

09:36.730 --> 09:38.330
do let us know in advance,

09:38.360 --> 09:39.360
so as to

09:39.380 --> 09:40.680
avoid misunderstandings.

09:42.080 --> 09:42.960
Okay.

09:45.520 --> 09:46.590
Zhao.

09:46.680 --> 09:48.570
What are you all talking about?

09:50.000 --> 09:51.290
Let's go back first.

09:52.570 --> 09:53.460
No.

10:05.920 --> 10:07.040
Ms. Furong.

10:07.070 --> 10:09.110
Our master is hosting a banquet tonight.

10:09.140 --> 10:10.410
He'd like to invite you for a dance.

10:11.220 --> 10:12.380
Zhao.

10:12.410 --> 10:14.170
Why are you in such a hurry?

10:14.190 --> 10:15.070
This is not a place to stay for long.

10:15.100 --> 10:15.890
We'll talk about it when we get back.

10:16.600 --> 10:18.600
I'm here on serious business.

10:20.410 --> 10:22.020
What kind of serious business would you have here?

10:22.050 --> 10:23.740
Uncle Bai will be angry if he finds out.

10:23.760 --> 10:24.590
Let's go back.

10:24.970 --> 10:25.730
No.

10:32.160 --> 10:33.300
Young man.

10:35.130 --> 10:37.100
Come and watch me dance next time.

10:43.520 --> 10:45.760
Didn't you go out of town for business?

10:45.790 --> 10:47.390
Why were you at Unbridled Pavilion?

10:47.390 --> 10:48.630
You happened to know the owner?

10:49.750 --> 10:50.600
No, I don't.

10:50.980 --> 10:51.920
You don't?

10:52.150 --> 10:54.030
But when you were talking to him just now,

10:54.050 --> 10:55.600
you guys were clearly speaking cryptically,

10:55.600 --> 10:56.750
as if there was common understanding.

10:56.750 --> 10:58.020
What about you, Shuo?

10:58.180 --> 10:59.330
What were you doing at Unbridled Pavilion?

11:00.500 --> 11:01.870
Master Sun directed me there.

11:01.900 --> 11:03.620
She said that the pavilion's owner is an immortal.

11:03.640 --> 11:04.790
An immortal?

11:05.290 --> 11:06.290
And you believe it?

11:06.780 --> 11:08.150
I initially didn't.

11:08.170 --> 11:09.250
But after testing him today,

11:09.280 --> 11:10.400
he actually does have some supernatural skill.

11:10.790 --> 11:11.550
Shuo.

11:11.580 --> 11:13.340
That Unbridled Pavilion is not a good place.

11:13.360 --> 11:14.790
I know you want to be an immortal,

11:14.810 --> 11:16.170
but they are all swindlers.

11:16.200 --> 11:17.690
Don't be fooled by them.

11:17.980 --> 11:19.760
You've always been kind to others.

11:19.790 --> 11:21.610
Why are you so hostile towards Unbridled Pavilion?

11:22.360 --> 11:23.600
Or...

11:23.620 --> 11:24.740
is there something you know?

11:26.270 --> 11:27.030
I...

11:27.480 --> 11:29.030
I'm just afraid that you'll be cheated.

11:30.270 --> 11:31.630
That's all?

11:31.970 --> 11:34.400
You're not hiding something from me, are you?

11:35.870 --> 11:36.910
No.

11:38.020 --> 11:39.110
It better be.

11:39.240 --> 11:39.960
As you know,

11:39.960 --> 11:41.480
I hate it when people lie to me.

11:42.440 --> 11:43.630
Our residence is right ahead.

11:43.630 --> 11:44.750
Go back early.

11:45.210 --> 11:46.680
I have something to do at the steamed bun stall.

11:46.710 --> 11:47.830
I'll be back later to keep you company.

11:52.960 --> 11:55.080
Zhao is acting weird today.

11:56.210 --> 11:56.960
That Fan Yue

11:56.960 --> 11:59.220
doesn't look like a decent immortal either.

11:59.340 --> 12:01.460
I must clarify with Master Sun.

12:03.620 --> 12:04.620
Master.

12:04.650 --> 12:06.800
Are we just going to let the kid from Eternal Race get away?

12:06.820 --> 12:08.500
If he spreads the news that us Demon Race has entered Ning'an City

12:08.550 --> 12:09.460
back to Lanling Sect,

12:09.490 --> 12:11.400
we won't be able to operate Unbridled Pavilion anymore.

12:11.420 --> 12:12.570
I really don't care about

12:12.600 --> 12:14.200
Lanling Sect, actually.

12:15.150 --> 12:17.240
What I’m interested in now

12:18.450 --> 12:19.880
is Bai Shuo.

12:20.520 --> 12:21.880
A human

12:21.900 --> 12:24.050
who can not only light up the Desireless Stone,

12:24.180 --> 12:26.660
but also engaged to someone from Lanling Sect.

12:27.180 --> 12:29.040
Don't you think it's interesting?

12:29.360 --> 12:30.240
Master.

12:30.710 --> 12:32.050
You mean...

12:32.470 --> 12:34.660
Bai Shuo could be a trap by the Eternals?

12:34.680 --> 12:35.790
Could they have already known

12:35.790 --> 12:37.550
you were the one who took the Desireless Stone?

12:38.100 --> 12:39.440
We'll know

12:39.710 --> 12:40.950
once we test it.

12:41.350 --> 12:43.110
If she is really an outcast of the Eternals,

12:43.130 --> 12:44.290
and had approached me

12:44.320 --> 12:45.840
to find out my secrets,

12:46.420 --> 12:47.560
I will

12:48.170 --> 12:51.410
give her a good home where her soul vanishes.

13:38.310 --> 13:39.920
Aren't demons supposed to eat people?

13:39.940 --> 13:41.660
He could easily slap me to death,

13:41.690 --> 13:43.210
so why does it seem like he's teasing me?

13:44.010 --> 13:45.640
We've passed by so many houses on the way,

13:45.660 --> 13:46.700
but he is going nowhere.

13:46.730 --> 13:48.010
He is only coming for me.

13:55.020 --> 13:57.420
The things given by Master Sun are really useless.

13:57.450 --> 13:58.880
This demon chased me all the way,

13:58.900 --> 14:00.190
but isn't trying to kill me.

14:00.220 --> 14:02.570
Is it a coincidence or is someone trying to test me?

14:03.850 --> 14:05.240
Grand Master, for your judgement.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.320
The Demon Race has entered Ning'an City

14:06.320 --> 14:07.600
and opened an Unbridled Pavilion for guests.

14:07.630 --> 14:09.020
Their purpose is currently unknown.

14:12.390 --> 14:13.510
Demonic aura?

14:25.440 --> 14:30.140
[Ruiyun Hall]

14:38.990 --> 14:40.580
As expected of the top courtesan!

15:32.520 --> 15:33.940
Shen, go!

15:34.720 --> 15:36.480
Go, Shen, go!

15:58.630 --> 15:59.910
What's going on?

15:59.910 --> 16:00.570
Shen!

16:36.950 --> 16:38.010
Young man.

16:39.970 --> 16:41.950
Come and watch me dance next time.

16:44.280 --> 16:45.250
It's you.

16:46.060 --> 16:47.800
The top courtesan of Unbridled Pavilion?

16:47.840 --> 16:49.470
So what?

16:49.490 --> 16:50.860
What exactly are you trying to do

16:50.890 --> 16:52.250
by infiltrating Ning'an City?

16:53.930 --> 16:55.310
As a demon,

16:56.560 --> 16:58.870
aren't we supposed to harm others?

16:59.160 --> 17:01.200
You're so stupidly funny

17:01.710 --> 17:03.260
for an immortal.

17:52.340 --> 17:53.050
[Unbridled Pavilion]

17:53.050 --> 17:57.380
[Closed]

17:55.960 --> 17:57.030
Master,

17:57.030 --> 17:58.590
we may now have this wolf demon.

17:58.630 --> 18:00.670
If Bai Shuo is a part of the Eternals,

18:00.690 --> 18:02.650
she would use magic at critical moments.

18:03.350 --> 18:05.150
But if she's just a human

18:05.170 --> 18:06.520
and we drive her to death,

18:06.600 --> 18:08.990
the plan to activate the Desireless Stone will be all in vain.

18:09.010 --> 18:11.230
I've placed a restraining curse on the wolf demon.

18:11.250 --> 18:12.630
It will only hurt, but never kill.

18:12.880 --> 18:14.630
It's enough to test Bai Shuo's capabilities.

18:15.420 --> 18:16.400
Boss!

18:21.250 --> 18:23.080
Boss, there's a demon!

18:23.100 --> 18:24.080
Why are you here?

18:25.170 --> 18:26.440
I'm having a bad year.

18:26.440 --> 18:27.810
I ran into a demon the minute I stepped out.

18:27.840 --> 18:28.400
My dear immortal,

18:28.420 --> 18:30.340
let's see if your Lanling magic is legit or not.

18:30.900 --> 18:31.960
Ms. Bai, didn't you

18:31.960 --> 18:33.560
think that I'm an evil person?

18:33.590 --> 18:34.590
Now that you are in trouble,

18:34.610 --> 18:36.240
you believe that I'm an immortal?

18:36.280 --> 18:37.080
Being an immortal doesn't count

18:37.110 --> 18:38.590
if all you can do is summon rain and thunder.

18:38.610 --> 18:39.850
The real test is whether you can help me tonight.

18:50.060 --> 18:51.820
Even in such grave danger,

18:51.850 --> 18:53.730
you're still looking to test me.

18:54.600 --> 18:56.100
You're quite bold.

18:59.990 --> 19:01.270
Don't blame me for not reminding you.

19:01.270 --> 19:02.270
This talisman of mine is useless.

19:02.270 --> 19:03.600
It's useless in your hands,

19:03.630 --> 19:05.000
but it's not in mine.

19:11.290 --> 19:12.250
Scram!

19:19.390 --> 19:20.670
So, am I

19:20.690 --> 19:21.890
a god or a demon?

19:23.230 --> 19:24.990
God, you're a god.

19:44.070 --> 19:45.550
When this wolf demon goes berserk,

19:45.550 --> 19:47.460
even two people can't take him down.

19:47.480 --> 19:49.460
That's no way to test something.

19:49.750 --> 19:51.590
It seems that they are not on the same side with the wolf demon.

19:51.930 --> 19:52.940
It's her blood.

19:53.750 --> 19:55.820
A talisman stained with human blood should subdue demons.

19:56.250 --> 19:58.490
Why is it that Bai Shuo’s blood enhances demonic power instead?

19:59.020 --> 20:00.440
Who is she exactly?

20:18.380 --> 20:19.420
The Desireless Stone.

20:23.670 --> 20:24.470
Stop!

20:42.470 --> 20:43.270
Master?

20:44.220 --> 20:45.350
Where did he go?

21:02.520 --> 21:07.480
[Lunar Hidden Sea]

21:14.770 --> 21:16.050
What is this place?

21:21.200 --> 21:22.360
Desireless Stone...

21:23.020 --> 21:24.890
What is this stone?

21:24.950 --> 21:26.630
How did it get into my body?

21:33.920 --> 21:34.780
Sir.

21:39.790 --> 21:40.750
Sir!

21:40.750 --> 21:41.790
Where am I?

21:41.790 --> 21:43.160
How can I get out?

21:54.160 --> 21:57.540
♫Across thousands of miles♫

21:57.120 --> 21:58.270
You're just a mere mortal

21:58.270 --> 21:59.790
who can't live beyond a hundred years.

22:00.510 --> 22:02.400
How can you repay me?

22:01.380 --> 22:05.760
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

22:09.220 --> 22:10.100
My benefactor?

22:09.630 --> 22:16.760
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

22:10.930 --> 22:11.650
Sir!

22:17.740 --> 22:22.670
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

22:24.880 --> 22:25.880
Hidden Sea?

22:26.720 --> 22:29.240
Is this the legendary Lunar Hidden Sea?

22:30.640 --> 22:32.470
How dare you run after stealing my stuff?

22:32.810 --> 22:33.970
Do you want to die?

22:35.170 --> 22:37.110
Boss, no matter what you do,

22:37.110 --> 22:38.160
please take me to the other side.

22:43.510 --> 22:44.510
Where did he go?

22:45.650 --> 22:47.200
He was there just now.

22:47.200 --> 22:48.780
Stop playing dumb.

22:48.810 --> 22:50.720
Return the Desireless Stone to me!

22:58.500 --> 22:59.790
I can't extract it out.

23:00.500 --> 23:01.790
It has recognized its master.

23:08.470 --> 23:09.750
The Desireless Stone is a divine object.

23:10.180 --> 23:11.830
There are no longer divine deities in this world.

23:11.860 --> 23:13.030
What grounds do you have to be its master?

23:15.790 --> 23:16.880
Tell me.

23:16.880 --> 23:18.100
Who are you?

23:22.790 --> 23:24.060
Look at this one.

23:24.720 --> 23:25.310
How about this?

23:25.310 --> 23:26.700
Is there any in plain color?

23:40.030 --> 23:40.960
Young Lord,

23:40.960 --> 23:42.480
we've successfully framed him.

23:42.480 --> 23:44.560
That Eternal is heading towards Unbridled Pavilion.

23:46.430 --> 23:48.110
Regardless of whoever dies or survives the fight

23:48.110 --> 23:49.590
between Lanling Sect and Bright Moon Palace,

23:49.590 --> 23:51.080
it will be beneficial to Cold Spring Palace.

23:51.100 --> 23:52.610
I'm actually looking forward

23:52.640 --> 23:54.440
to this chaotic battle.

23:55.110 --> 23:56.640
I'm looking forward to it too.

24:00.460 --> 24:01.310
Master.

24:02.070 --> 24:02.970
Master?

24:03.440 --> 24:04.330
Master!

24:04.880 --> 24:05.680
Master!

24:07.190 --> 24:07.930
Master!

24:08.880 --> 24:09.640
Master!

24:10.390 --> 24:10.880
Master!

24:10.880 --> 24:11.720
Stop shouting.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.920
Master and her were taken away by the Desireless Stone.

24:13.920 --> 24:15.560
It's a divine object. There's no point looking for them.

24:18.680 --> 24:19.640
Then what should we do?

24:20.720 --> 24:21.570
Dear immortal...

24:21.880 --> 24:22.920
I don’t have time

24:22.920 --> 24:24.470
to continue playing games with you.

24:24.500 --> 24:25.970
Tell me, who are you?

24:25.990 --> 24:27.880
How did you get a divine object to recognize you as its master?

24:27.910 --> 24:29.460
How could you have entered this divine realm?

24:31.110 --> 24:33.040
That stone is a divine object?

24:33.070 --> 24:34.030
Just now...

24:34.090 --> 24:35.290
he was trying to kill me?

24:36.850 --> 24:38.810
I don't know what you're talking about.

24:38.930 --> 24:40.210
What divine object?

24:40.280 --> 24:41.610
What divine realm?

24:41.380 --> 24:45.190
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

24:41.630 --> 24:43.670
I merely wanted to seek guidance on the pursuit of enlightenment.

24:43.750 --> 24:45.030
I am Bai Shuo.

24:45.450 --> 24:46.720
Stubborn.

24:46.750 --> 24:47.720
Great.

24:47.880 --> 24:48.840
If you die,

24:49.460 --> 24:54.820
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees♫

24:49.500 --> 24:50.870
the Desireless Stone will come out.

24:57.510 --> 25:04.630
♫ To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart ♫

25:05.270 --> 25:10.440
♫I'm your wanderer♫

25:18.950 --> 25:19.780
Master!

25:20.360 --> 25:20.960
Master!

25:22.020 --> 25:22.830
Wait.

25:24.610 --> 25:25.850
Something is wrong with our master.

25:28.690 --> 25:32.080
Can you... save me first?

25:39.690 --> 25:40.880
Oh no,

25:40.910 --> 25:43.050
Master's Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal is acting up.

25:46.820 --> 25:48.580
Kill her!

25:48.600 --> 25:49.580
Wait.

25:50.000 --> 25:51.970
Your master was injured by me.

25:52.000 --> 25:52.680
If you want to kill me,

25:52.680 --> 25:54.400
you'll have to see if you've got what it takes.

25:54.400 --> 25:55.200
Kill her!

25:55.200 --> 25:56.000
Wait.

25:56.710 --> 25:58.230
You said it yourself.

25:58.330 --> 25:59.400
The Desireless Stone is a divine object.

25:59.430 --> 26:00.560
If it recognizes me as its master,

26:00.580 --> 26:02.120
it means I'm definitely not an ordinary person.

26:02.200 --> 26:02.920
Fan Yue.

26:02.920 --> 26:04.310
I don't know who you are,

26:04.330 --> 26:06.330
and I don't know why you came to Ning'an City.

26:06.360 --> 26:07.470
But I'm sure that

26:07.490 --> 26:08.970
the Desireless Stone is very important to you.

26:09.000 --> 26:09.800
Did you really think

26:09.830 --> 26:10.830
I wouldn't kill you because of this?

26:10.830 --> 26:11.640
Of course you will.

26:12.540 --> 26:14.580
But killing me won't do you any good.

26:14.610 --> 26:15.960
What I want to negotiate with you

26:15.980 --> 26:16.780
is a deal.

26:16.810 --> 26:17.940
As a mere human,

26:18.310 --> 26:20.570
what qualifies you to strike a deal with me?

26:20.730 --> 26:22.360
An ordinary human wouldn't dare.

26:22.380 --> 26:23.450
But I'm different.

26:23.830 --> 26:24.790
Whatever it is you aim to accomplish,

26:24.790 --> 26:25.720
I'll help you with it.

26:26.480 --> 26:27.530
But you have to help me too.

26:27.550 --> 26:28.980
What can I help you with?

26:29.010 --> 26:30.770
Help me go back to that place,

26:30.790 --> 26:32.230
and find someone very important to me.

26:41.090 --> 26:41.790
Zhao.

26:44.840 --> 26:45.630
Uncle Bai.

26:46.610 --> 26:47.930
When did you return to the city?

26:48.110 --> 26:49.350
Why are you here so late?

26:51.730 --> 26:52.180
I...

26:55.030 --> 26:55.830
Chong Zhao.

26:56.440 --> 26:58.070
I raised you up.

26:58.070 --> 27:00.440
When did you pick up the habit of visiting brothels?

27:01.900 --> 27:03.140
Uncle Bai, I haven't.

27:03.240 --> 27:04.270
I'm looking for someone.

27:04.270 --> 27:05.070
Who isn't here

27:05.790 --> 27:06.680
to look for someone?

27:09.460 --> 27:10.410
Who are you looking for?

27:12.330 --> 27:14.190
Don't tell me Bai Shuo is also inside?

27:14.600 --> 27:15.360
No.

27:15.510 --> 27:16.510
That brat.

27:16.510 --> 27:17.350
How dare she visits a place like this?

27:17.350 --> 27:18.880
I'll break her legs!

27:18.880 --> 27:20.510
Oh no, there are demons everywhere inside.

27:20.510 --> 27:22.240
If we run into them, Uncle Bai...

27:23.960 --> 27:26.200
What did you see in the Lunar Hidden Sea?

27:26.460 --> 27:28.510
Someone who once saved my life.

27:28.540 --> 27:29.930
He was inside.

27:29.950 --> 27:31.550
It doesn't seem like she's lying.

27:32.340 --> 27:34.370
But if someone exists in the Lunar Hidden Sea,

27:35.390 --> 27:37.560
does that mean the Divine Race still exists in this world?

27:38.440 --> 27:40.630
Is that the reason why the Desireless Stone chose her?

27:40.680 --> 27:42.160
To try and strike a deal with me...

27:42.310 --> 27:43.440
Aren’t you afraid of death?

27:43.730 --> 27:44.520
Yes, I am.

27:45.330 --> 27:47.400
Humans may not be able to live beyond a hundred years,

27:47.420 --> 27:49.140
but my benefactor is an immortal.

27:49.170 --> 27:50.300
I may be afraid of death.

27:50.320 --> 27:52.160
But I'm more afraid of not having a chance to repay him.

27:52.190 --> 27:53.870
So even if I am being used by you,

27:53.890 --> 27:55.670
I'll never expose your identity.

27:55.700 --> 27:57.260
But it must be an equal exchange,

27:57.610 --> 27:58.560
and you must fulfill my wish.

27:59.150 --> 28:00.470
Why should I believe you?

28:00.490 --> 28:01.970
You claimed that you are capable.

28:02.060 --> 28:04.440
I'm just a mere mortal, so what is there to fear?

28:05.300 --> 28:06.310
Open the door!

28:06.650 --> 28:07.410
Uncle Bai.

28:07.440 --> 28:08.780
-Uncle Bai, calm down.
-Open the door!

28:08.830 --> 28:09.640
-Uncle Bai!
-If you don't open the door,

28:08.850 --> 28:10.540
[Unbridled Pavilion]

28:09.640 --> 28:10.790
I will break it down!

28:10.790 --> 28:12.270
-Calm down, Uncle Bai.
-Open the door!

28:12.680 --> 28:14.000
It's my father.

28:14.000 --> 28:15.510
Why is he here at this hour?

28:15.510 --> 28:17.200
Fan Yue is most likely a demon.

28:17.220 --> 28:19.620
These two next to him are no good either.

28:19.650 --> 28:20.970
If there's a conflict,

28:20.990 --> 28:22.560
they might not hurt me,

28:22.590 --> 28:23.900
but my father will be the one to suffer.

28:24.540 --> 28:25.160
Bai Shuo!

28:25.160 --> 28:26.720
Give our cooperation some more thought.

28:26.720 --> 28:27.640
My father is the city's governor.

28:27.640 --> 28:29.240
It won't be any good if he

28:29.240 --> 28:29.920
sees you like this.

28:29.920 --> 28:30.950
Let’s avoid him for now.

28:31.000 --> 28:32.740
You want me to avoid a human?

28:32.760 --> 28:33.880
Our human rules state that

28:33.880 --> 28:35.260
the city's governor is the most important.

28:35.290 --> 28:36.160
If you offend my father,

28:36.160 --> 28:37.440
no matter what your plans are,

28:37.440 --> 28:39.160
you wouldn't be able to continue operating here.

28:41.330 --> 28:42.530
Your master is unwell.

28:42.560 --> 28:43.470
Take good care of him.

28:43.550 --> 28:44.640
Don't let him speak.

28:46.470 --> 28:47.530
Don't go downstairs.

28:53.350 --> 28:53.980
Check the building.

28:54.000 --> 28:55.480
Uncle Bai, calm down.

28:55.510 --> 28:56.550
Say nothing!

28:57.460 --> 28:58.110
Calm down!

28:58.110 --> 28:59.030
Don't stop me!

28:59.500 --> 29:00.740
I told you not to speak!

29:00.790 --> 29:01.400
Uncle Bai!

29:01.400 --> 29:02.960
Little brat.

29:03.550 --> 29:04.320
Uncle Bai.

29:04.340 --> 29:05.840
How dare a mere human

29:06.080 --> 29:07.870
-threaten me like this!
-Master!

29:08.330 --> 29:09.330
Master.

29:09.360 --> 29:10.520
Bai Shuo said

29:10.540 --> 29:11.140
we mustn't make a sound

29:11.170 --> 29:12.180
or go downstairs.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.230
Father.

29:27.820 --> 29:28.720
What a coincidence.

29:28.720 --> 29:29.750
You're here to have fun too?

29:29.750 --> 29:31.160
I’m not fooling with you!

29:31.160 --> 29:31.920
Little brat.

29:31.920 --> 29:32.970
Come here!

29:34.510 --> 29:35.800
How dare you scold me?

29:36.030 --> 29:37.400
You brought so many people to the brothel.

29:37.400 --> 29:38.820
How can you answer to my late mother?

29:39.390 --> 29:41.110
I'm here to patrol!

29:41.130 --> 29:42.760
Do you think we have nothing better to do?

29:43.110 --> 29:44.070
Brat,

29:44.070 --> 29:45.640
I'll beat you to death today.

29:45.640 --> 29:46.440
-Move aside!
-Uncle Bai.

29:46.440 --> 29:47.400
Move! Move!

29:47.680 --> 29:48.470
-No, no.
-Move away!

29:48.500 --> 29:49.460
Uncle Bai.

29:49.480 --> 29:50.570
I have something to tell you.

29:50.600 --> 29:51.550
We'll talk later.

29:51.590 --> 29:52.240
Uncle Bai!

29:52.240 --> 29:53.590
I must say it now.

29:53.760 --> 29:54.590
Fine, speak.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.900
My engagement with Shuo was arranged long ago.

29:57.930 --> 29:59.200
I had wanted to be successful

29:59.200 --> 30:00.570
so that I can take good care of her.

30:00.590 --> 30:02.350
But I don't want to wait anymore, Uncle Bai.

30:02.880 --> 30:04.030
Will you honor the engagement

30:04.490 --> 30:05.720
and let Shuo marry me?

30:14.670 --> 30:15.930
Good chap.

30:16.820 --> 30:18.300
After so many years,

30:18.330 --> 30:20.610
I finally got you to say that.

30:22.500 --> 30:23.500
Let's go home.

30:23.520 --> 30:25.270
Let's get drunk today!

30:25.390 --> 30:26.740
Let's go home and drink.

30:29.560 --> 30:30.670
Little brat.

30:31.400 --> 30:32.150
Go home.

30:33.630 --> 30:34.470
Let's go.

30:37.640 --> 30:39.510
You’ve finally wised up, huh?

30:58.910 --> 30:59.590
Master.

31:00.100 --> 31:00.790
Master!

31:00.790 --> 31:01.880
-Master!
-Master!

31:26.350 --> 31:27.510
He's good at disguise.

31:39.890 --> 31:41.710
He can teleport.

31:45.750 --> 31:47.440
He's cruel and bloodthirsty.

31:50.680 --> 31:51.400
A demon?

31:52.440 --> 31:53.830
If Fan Yue is really a demon,

31:53.830 --> 31:54.870
it's hard to say if he won't

31:54.900 --> 31:56.620
get me in trouble after he recovers.

31:56.640 --> 31:57.920
Or even...

31:59.720 --> 32:00.640
If you die,

32:01.240 --> 32:02.880
the Desireless Stone will come out.

32:05.920 --> 32:07.200
Or even kill me.

32:08.160 --> 32:10.020
I may have negotiated a deal for now,

32:10.050 --> 32:11.570
but I still have to be careful.

32:44.570 --> 32:45.570
Such bad luck.

32:45.600 --> 32:46.470
Why are you crying?

32:46.490 --> 32:47.460
Our master is not dead.

32:48.440 --> 32:50.170
The Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on him

32:50.200 --> 32:51.710
will burn his heart and soul every time it acts up.

32:51.730 --> 32:52.770
It's unbearable pain.

32:52.800 --> 32:54.280
This is already the forth time.

32:54.310 --> 32:55.510
If it keeps happening, he will...

32:55.540 --> 32:56.740
As long as he can activate the Desireless Stone

32:56.790 --> 32:58.150
and obtain its divine power,

32:58.170 --> 32:59.740
Master will definitely survive.

33:00.320 --> 33:02.110
But this is just a legend of the world.

33:02.110 --> 33:03.440
Will it really work?

33:03.440 --> 33:05.520
Before, when the Desireless Stone laid dormant,

33:05.710 --> 33:07.230
I still had my suspicions.

33:07.620 --> 33:09.340
But now that the Desireless Stone had been activated

33:09.370 --> 33:10.970
and entered Bai Shuo's body,

33:11.060 --> 33:12.540
that means it's possible.

33:14.440 --> 33:16.160
I'll go get Bai Shuo now.

33:16.190 --> 33:16.750
Stop!

33:16.790 --> 33:18.180
What's the point of getting her now?

33:18.220 --> 33:19.000
If we can't gather all Five Contemplations,

33:19.000 --> 33:19.880
we can't activate the Desireless Stone

33:19.880 --> 33:21.290
and still won't be able to save Master's life.

33:21.720 --> 33:23.510
There are still three stars left.

33:23.510 --> 33:24.650
We still have a chance.

33:24.680 --> 33:26.570
We mustn't raise anymore alarms

33:26.590 --> 33:28.430
and let Bai Shuo gain more leverage.

33:28.460 --> 33:29.220
Understand?

33:43.290 --> 33:44.640
It's your birthday present.

33:44.660 --> 33:45.750
Open and take a look.

33:45.770 --> 33:46.720
What is it?

33:46.740 --> 33:47.670
So mysterious.

33:50.390 --> 33:52.090
How did you know I wanted this?

33:52.400 --> 33:53.480
I'm your sister.

33:53.480 --> 33:54.640
Of course I know.

33:54.640 --> 33:57.240
This dagger was made by the masters in the temple.

33:57.240 --> 33:58.640
It can repel and avoid evil.

33:58.640 --> 34:00.680
I wish you good luck in all your future endeavors,

34:00.680 --> 34:01.930
where you'll turn misfortune into fortune.

34:01.960 --> 34:03.200
Turn misfortune into fortune?

34:03.790 --> 34:04.400
Xi,

34:04.400 --> 34:05.810
I have a question for you.

34:05.880 --> 34:08.110
Do you really not remember

34:08.110 --> 34:09.510
the last time when we met an immortal?

34:15.139 --> 34:16.630
But as long as you think so,

34:16.630 --> 34:17.400
I'll believe you.

34:18.030 --> 34:20.670
But they all said I had gone crazy.

34:21.290 --> 34:22.820
Don't care what others say.

34:22.840 --> 34:24.239
Just do what you want.

34:24.270 --> 34:26.550
Remember what Mother used to say?

34:26.730 --> 34:27.960
I'm Chenxi.

34:27.989 --> 34:29.360
You're Xingyue.

34:29.380 --> 34:30.699
The stars shine brightly

34:30.730 --> 34:32.239
as the moon emerges from the clouds.

34:32.370 --> 34:33.610
Our dearest Shuo

34:33.639 --> 34:35.730
will be like the stars and moon in the sky,

34:35.750 --> 34:37.949
shining where it is darkest.

34:38.699 --> 34:40.300
Today is my birthday.

34:40.330 --> 34:42.159
Do you really have to make me cry?

34:42.179 --> 34:44.130
I'm serious, Shuo.

34:44.150 --> 34:46.790
If you've made up your mind, just go for it.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.699
I'll always be behind you.

34:49.290 --> 34:50.520
Thank you, Sister.

34:59.390 --> 35:00.350
Xi.

35:01.060 --> 35:02.980
I think I really met a demon.

35:03.070 --> 35:05.200
He said the Desireless Stone is a divine stone.

35:05.490 --> 35:06.550
But why did a divine stone

35:06.550 --> 35:08.110
enter my human body?

35:09.250 --> 35:11.210
Also, I met my benefactor today.

35:17.590 --> 35:19.430
The Desireless Stone belongs to Fan Yue.

35:20.210 --> 35:21.850
Could he be related to my benefactor?

35:23.060 --> 35:25.270
Is this guidance from my benefactor

35:25.520 --> 35:27.330
or a ruse by Fan Yue?

35:36.610 --> 35:37.450
Zhao.

35:38.140 --> 35:39.540
Have you finished drinking with my father?

35:40.400 --> 35:41.430
Shuo.

35:41.770 --> 35:42.890
Let's talk.

35:45.180 --> 35:46.660
Thank you for today.

35:46.690 --> 35:48.020
You even mentioned the proposal

35:48.050 --> 35:49.920
to help me get out of that situation.

35:49.940 --> 35:51.740
I owe you a big favor this time.

35:53.070 --> 35:54.920
What if I'm not just trying to help you?

35:56.190 --> 35:58.660
Are you serious about marrying me?

35:58.930 --> 36:00.840
You know how bad my reputation is

36:00.840 --> 36:01.840
in this city.

36:01.890 --> 36:03.230
Are you out of your mind?

36:05.260 --> 36:07.020
I just want to take care of you.

36:07.050 --> 36:08.820
With that frail body of yours,

36:08.840 --> 36:10.510
maybe let me take care of you instead

36:10.540 --> 36:11.560
when I achieve immortality.

36:12.150 --> 36:13.380
But Shuo,

36:13.410 --> 36:14.400
the boss of Unbridled Pavilion

36:14.400 --> 36:15.920
doesn't look like a deity at all.

36:15.940 --> 36:17.670
Don't be fooled by him.

36:17.840 --> 36:19.360
Zhao is simple and weak.

36:19.360 --> 36:21.560
Apart from making steamed buns, he knows nothing about martial arts.

36:21.580 --> 36:22.960
It's better to not get him involved

36:22.960 --> 36:24.030
in these dangerous matters.

36:24.540 --> 36:25.630
Don't worry.

36:25.660 --> 36:27.180
I won't trust him easily.

36:27.200 --> 36:29.110
I'll take care of it.

36:29.880 --> 36:30.800
It's getting late.

36:30.800 --> 36:31.760
I'm going to bed.

36:31.850 --> 36:33.000
You too.

36:33.000 --> 36:33.630
Don't tire yourself out.

36:36.800 --> 36:37.590
Wait.

36:42.230 --> 36:43.620
There's something in Shuo's body.

36:43.640 --> 36:44.520
What's wrong?

36:45.600 --> 36:46.550
Nothing.

36:47.120 --> 36:48.200
Go back and rest.

37:00.260 --> 37:01.680
The Desireless Stone?

37:02.170 --> 37:03.810
Why is it in Shuo's body?

37:07.880 --> 37:08.840
Zhao.

37:09.320 --> 37:10.570
What's wrong with you?

37:11.150 --> 37:12.880
I can't let Shuo find out that I'm an Eternal.

37:12.900 --> 37:14.150
I can't extract it out now.

37:17.730 --> 37:18.770
I'm fine.

37:18.800 --> 37:20.150
I'm just too sleepy.

37:20.170 --> 37:21.130
Go back and rest.

37:21.160 --> 37:22.370
I’m going back.

37:30.110 --> 37:32.540
Zhao is being weird today.

38:06.180 --> 38:07.540
I actually can't extract it out.

38:08.290 --> 38:09.920
Shuo went to Unbridled Pavilion

38:09.950 --> 38:11.800
and came back with the Desireless Stone.

38:12.400 --> 38:13.150
The demons in Unbridled Pavilion

38:13.150 --> 38:15.000
must have something to do with the Desireless Stone going missing.

38:16.100 --> 38:17.230
But why did the Desireless Stone

38:17.230 --> 38:19.100
recognized Shuo as its master when she's just human?

38:19.500 --> 38:20.980
I wouldn't know if it's a blessing or a curse

38:21.070 --> 38:22.670
if the Eternals know about this.

38:23.650 --> 38:25.360
I mustn't report it rashly.

38:38.060 --> 38:40.150
This pill can only temporarily relieve the pain.

38:40.190 --> 38:41.400
It can't cure the symptoms.

38:41.430 --> 38:43.350
We need to gather the Five Contemplations as soon as possible.

38:44.040 --> 38:46.370
Back then, the deities perished in the Divine War against the Hidden Lord.

38:46.390 --> 38:47.420
The Divine Region collapsed,

38:47.440 --> 38:48.850
and the Divine Realm ceased to exist in this world.

38:49.490 --> 38:50.510
Legend has it that the Lunar Hidden Sea

38:50.510 --> 38:52.590
is where Goddess Xingyue of the Lunar Race cultivates.

38:52.940 --> 38:53.790
For the past 60,000 years,

38:53.810 --> 38:55.720
no one has ever found it,

38:55.750 --> 38:56.910
let alone go inside.

38:56.930 --> 38:58.600
Exactly who is this Bai Shuo?

38:59.190 --> 39:01.140
Desireless Stone is Xingyue's divine stone.

39:01.830 --> 39:02.480
It's very likely that

39:02.480 --> 39:04.590
the Desireless Stone was what brought us into the Lunar Hidden Sea.

39:04.960 --> 39:07.290
She can activate the Desireless Stone at the critical moment.

39:07.940 --> 39:10.620
Her blood can also increase the wolf demon's power.

39:10.640 --> 39:12.140
No matter who she is,

39:12.180 --> 39:14.620
she must have secrets that I don’t know.

39:15.090 --> 39:16.930
But when I probed again yesterday,

39:17.670 --> 39:19.030
the aura around her

39:19.420 --> 39:20.890
is indeed a human's.

39:21.190 --> 39:22.280
Bai Shuo's identity

39:22.760 --> 39:23.680
is a mystery.

39:23.710 --> 39:24.990
Yet, she has many tricks.

39:25.790 --> 39:27.140
After just two or three interactions,

39:27.160 --> 39:29.340
she has roughly figured out my plans.

39:29.360 --> 39:30.560
Our priority

39:30.980 --> 39:32.500
is to find a way

39:32.560 --> 39:33.920
to bring her back to Bright Moon Palace.

39:33.950 --> 39:35.160
But Master,

39:35.180 --> 39:36.740
you failed to extract the stone yesterday.

39:36.770 --> 39:38.160
I'm afraid she's already prepared.

39:38.950 --> 39:40.550
What if we give her

39:42.150 --> 39:44.650
a reason she can't refuse?

39:55.950 --> 39:57.280
What is the best tool to use

39:57.310 --> 39:58.460
to subdue demons?

39:59.800 --> 40:01.510
But none of these has never worked.

40:01.550 --> 40:02.590
Will it work?

40:08.190 --> 40:10.140
[Invitation]

40:13.550 --> 40:16.400
We'll close the pavilion at 5 p.m. today

40:16.420 --> 40:18.220
as we're looking forward to speaking with you.

40:18.250 --> 40:20.000
Speak with me?

40:26.350 --> 40:27.870
Whether you are a deity or a demon,

40:27.890 --> 40:29.410
I have to meet you again.

40:34.950 --> 40:36.050
You're saying

40:36.240 --> 40:37.550
you know my benefactor?

40:37.570 --> 40:38.530
Of course.

40:39.030 --> 40:39.880
Otherwise,

40:39.880 --> 40:41.970
I wouldn't have travelled around with the Desireless Stone.

40:42.090 --> 40:44.780
It's all to save my best friend.

40:44.850 --> 40:46.660
Previously, I thought it was strange too.

40:46.690 --> 40:49.080
How can a human control the Desireless Stone?

40:49.730 --> 40:50.730
But you said

40:50.750 --> 40:52.620
my friend is your benefactor.

40:52.730 --> 40:54.000
Then it all makes sense.

40:58.850 --> 41:01.440
Do you really think I'm a fool?

41:01.480 --> 41:03.240
Yesterday, we were about to kill each other.

41:03.260 --> 41:04.970
And now, when trouble strikes,

41:05.080 --> 41:06.560
aren't we supposed to be turning against each other?

41:06.920 --> 41:08.500
The Lunar Hidden Sea is a Divine Realm.

41:08.530 --> 41:09.970
There are no divine deities in this world.

41:10.230 --> 41:11.660
You could enter the last time

41:11.740 --> 41:14.350
as the Desireless Stone was accidentally activated.

41:14.600 --> 41:16.180
If you want to enter the Lunar Hidden Sea again,

41:16.380 --> 41:18.270
you have to activate the Desireless Stone.

41:18.890 --> 41:20.150
I don't want to believe either

41:20.150 --> 41:22.130
that the Desireless Stone chose a human.

41:22.180 --> 41:23.850
But that's the truth.

41:23.890 --> 41:26.360
In order to save my best friend,

41:26.560 --> 41:28.810
I can only cooperate with

41:28.840 --> 41:30.100
a mere mortal like you.

41:30.590 --> 41:32.000
Since there are no divine deities in the world,

41:32.000 --> 41:33.590
and no one can enter the Lunar Hidden Sea,

41:33.620 --> 41:36.270
then why is my benefactor trapped?

41:36.290 --> 41:37.480
Since you know him,

41:37.510 --> 41:38.480
you must know the reason.

41:39.150 --> 41:40.880
Ms. Bai keeps claiming

41:40.880 --> 41:43.110
that my friend is your benefactor.

41:43.680 --> 41:45.140
How would I know

41:45.400 --> 41:47.270
you are not lying?

41:47.420 --> 41:48.620
On what grounds

41:50.900 --> 41:52.640
should I share all of this with you?

41:54.050 --> 41:56.130
Since you and I have the same goal

41:56.160 --> 41:57.210
to some extent,

41:57.230 --> 41:58.540
there's indeed no need to investigate.

41:59.630 --> 42:01.030
What should I do

42:01.050 --> 42:02.150
to activate the Desireless Stone?

42:02.670 --> 42:04.310
You're quite straightforward, Ms. Bai.

42:04.910 --> 42:05.910
However,

42:06.690 --> 42:08.370
aren't you afraid

42:09.560 --> 42:10.700
that I'm a demon?

42:12.530 --> 42:14.140
I wouldn't say that I am completely unafraid.

42:14.520 --> 42:16.000
From last night to this morning,

42:16.030 --> 42:17.470
I've been thinking,

42:17.780 --> 42:19.010
if you are a demon,

42:19.040 --> 42:21.120
how should I keep you in check?

42:22.130 --> 42:23.380
In my sleeve,

42:23.410 --> 42:25.330
I've hidden a knife that is meant to kill you.

42:25.920 --> 42:27.850
But that seems too naive.

42:28.580 --> 42:30.940
Demon kills human, human kills demon.

42:30.960 --> 42:32.290
It's easy to tell

42:32.320 --> 42:33.280
who will win.

42:33.560 --> 42:35.770
So as we've said before,

42:35.790 --> 42:37.150
let's make a deal.

42:37.190 --> 42:38.580
Whether you are a god

42:38.830 --> 42:39.940
or a demon,

42:40.140 --> 42:41.490
I wouldn't ask about your origin

42:41.520 --> 42:44.080
nor care about who you really are.

42:44.100 --> 42:45.670
As long as you can save my benefactor,

42:45.730 --> 42:46.890
I will cooperate with you.

42:47.860 --> 42:48.620
Not bad.

42:49.590 --> 42:50.720
A wise man

42:51.260 --> 42:52.570
will live longer.

42:53.050 --> 42:54.490
The Desireless Stone is a divine object.

42:54.510 --> 42:56.120
To activate the Desireless Stone,

42:56.150 --> 42:57.190
must be gather

42:57.210 --> 43:01.900
the Five Contemplations of love, hate, kill, greed,

43:01.940 --> 43:02.860
and benevolence.

43:03.180 --> 43:04.010
Contemplations?

43:05.440 --> 43:07.350
These are so intangible.

43:07.370 --> 43:09.560
How should I gather it? Where should I go?

43:09.590 --> 43:11.630
We will depart

43:11.650 --> 43:13.260
for the Infinite Cosmos immediately.

43:11.880 --> 43:15.610
♫The person standing far away♫

43:13.890 --> 43:16.250
One word from you, and you want me to leave my hometown

43:16.360 --> 43:17.400
and come with you?

43:16.610 --> 43:18.970
♫Don't be afraid♫

43:18.110 --> 43:19.320
You've been seeking immortality for ten years,

43:19.270 --> 43:23.930
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

43:19.320 --> 43:20.960
but you found no way out.

43:20.960 --> 43:24.280
After wasting so much time, energy and money,

43:24.280 --> 43:27.030
you still know little about matters relating to deities and demons.

43:24.540 --> 43:31.060
♫Walk towards me♫

43:27.030 --> 43:29.320
You really think you can save someone with those

43:29.320 --> 43:30.710
human-made fairy tales?

43:30.710 --> 43:31.800
Dream on.

43:32.430 --> 43:34.510
Whether you believe me or not,

43:32.650 --> 43:36.000
♫My heart feels so...♫

43:34.510 --> 43:36.640
I am your only choice.

43:36.470 --> 43:42.370
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

43:36.880 --> 43:39.590
You know that very well.

43:40.110 --> 43:41.030
Of course.

43:42.120 --> 43:43.480
If you don't believe me,

43:43.900 --> 43:48.070
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

43:46.990 --> 43:48.200
you can stay.

43:51.150 --> 43:52.550
With my benefactor stuck,

43:51.410 --> 43:54.900
♫You are my distant call♫

43:52.570 --> 43:53.610
I'm the only one who can save him.

43:54.400 --> 43:57.110
If I want to save him, I must leave Ning'an City.

43:55.370 --> 43:59.790
♫You are my first and last♫

43:57.110 --> 43:58.880
You're not a good person,

43:58.880 --> 44:01.100
yet you dragged me into a game that I have to play.

44:01.320 --> 44:02.280
Three days.

44:02.760 --> 44:04.190
I'll give you an answer in three days.

44:04.440 --> 44:06.320
Why exactly three days?

44:06.520 --> 44:07.840
You've seen my father.

44:08.110 --> 44:09.880
I've been seeking immortality all these years.

44:09.880 --> 44:11.570
I've already made him angry enough.

44:11.800 --> 44:12.800
I can't be a dutiful daughter

44:12.800 --> 44:14.100
if I want to return the favor.

44:14.240 --> 44:15.550
I owe it to him.

44:15.590 --> 44:17.530
My father's birthday is in three days.

44:17.930 --> 44:19.150
Regardless whether I leave or not,

44:19.350 --> 44:21.390
I want to celebrate his birthday with him.

44:21.790 --> 44:23.210
Humans are troublesome.

44:24.110 --> 44:25.190
You're not human.

44:25.190 --> 44:26.280
Of course you don't understand.

44:26.410 --> 44:28.240
Life is barely a hundred years long.

44:28.510 --> 44:29.800
Every birthday

44:29.880 --> 44:31.950
should be spent well.

44:32.170 --> 44:33.580
If I really leave,

44:33.750 --> 44:36.270
I don't know when I'll be back.

44:36.290 --> 44:38.040
I should have a proper farewell with him,

44:38.070 --> 44:39.110
isn't it?
